def test_remember_nonascii_token(self):
        helper = self._makeOne('secret')
        request = self._makeRequest()
        la = text_(b'La Pe\xc3\xb1a', 'utf-8')
        self.assertRaises(
            ValueError, helper.remember, request, 'other', tokens=(la,)
        )
